Welcome to the MVS Ted Talk! Join our speakers Velma, Finn, and Jake as they breakdown PvE Rifts Mode.

MultiVersus is a free-to-play platform fighter with an ever-expanding cast of iconic characters and legendary universes, various online modes, in-game events, on-going content-filled seasons, and more.
title: MultiVersus - Official PvE Rifts Mode Overview Trailer

description:
The fast arena shooter you've been waiting for has arrived! XDefiant drops on May 21 on Playstation 5, XBox Series X/S and Ubisoft Connect PC. 

Ubisoft's worlds collide in a free-to-play, first-person arena shooter where you compete to be the best in fast-paced online matches! 

Join an always-evolving experience with regular updates bringing new playable factions and a growing collection of maps, weapons, and game modes. With cross-play, you will be able to join your friends across available platforms.

#Ubisoft #XDefiant
title: XDefiant - Official Launch Trailer

description: As of May 14th, 2024, the Killing Floor franchise is officially 15 years old! Join the Tripwire development team as they recount the steps they took to grow Killing Floor from a highly-addictive Unreal mod into the zed-slaying cooperative shooter franchise it is today. Then take a sneak peek at what's to come for Killing Floor 3!
title: Killing Floor 3 - Killing Floor 15th Anniversary Developer Diary
